{"tid":949140,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手遊記] 帶兩老去關西睇紅葉","createTime":"2018-12-20T15:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T15:30:02.000Z","uid":11254,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dd9f04c470dec696abfa1f41f8eae4a1741e8a84","tid":949140,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:02:11.000Z","msg":"第一次開POST 打遊記 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果識我唔好起底 多謝合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人都會覺得同屋企人去旅行好麻煩 可能會又呢樣唔食 個到又唔行咁<br />\n但我老豆老母都唔會 加上由細到大佢地都會帶我去旅行 <br />\n所以慣左無乜野 今次就由我帶佢地去睇紅葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行程<br />\nDAY 1 關西機場-&gt;城崎溫泉 住城崎溫泉 <br />\nDAY 2 城崎溫泉-&gt;竹田城跡(天空之城)  住和田山<br />\nDAY 3上午去立雲峽 睇雲海 下午去姬路城 住姬路<br />\nDAY 4 姬路-&gt;有馬溫泉 住有馬溫泉<br />\nDAY 5有馬溫泉-&gt; 神戶 神戶牛午餐  六甲山夜景<br />\nDAY 6 神戶&gt;京都 琉璃光院 詩仙堂 貴船神社 住京都 <br />\nDAY 7 東福寺 平等院 宇治 住大阪<br />\nDAY 8 箕面公園 新世界Spa World  -&gt;關西機場<br />\n<br />\n頭五日用關西廣域鐵路周遊券 尾三日用KTP<br />\n好多人覺得成日搬酒店好麻煩 但我習慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n同埋我好少買野 所以行李都唔洗點執<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90dd7e8d1151311224502b2082147de49e60e144","tid":949140,"uid":11254,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:02:54.000Z","msg":"DAY 1 <br />\n今次坐凌晨機  直接由關西機場去城崎溫泉<br />\n買個早餐先 最鐘意食個蛋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jKrN6uE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjKrN6uE.png&h=de665292&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關西空港 08:15&gt;09:28 大阪 <br />\n大阪09:38&gt;12:27 城崎溫泉  (ＪＲ特急はまかぜ1号・)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0k2Nm2Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0k2Nm2Z.png&h=f6db8f67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到城崎溫泉就12點半 岩岩好食LUNCH<br />\n11月去城崎溫泉 最出名就係食蟹 當然要食返夠本啦 <br />\n去左一間叫 いなば鮮魚店  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.inabasengyo.com/service.html#service02\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inabasengyo.com%2Fservice.html%23service02&d=fuxLroCnnWUwqjsasrgK4MVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=b0279507\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.inabasengyo.com/service.html#service02</a><br />\n佢個舖唔大 同埋無人招呼你 係用自動販賣機<br />\n買完等佢叫NUMBER <br />\nかにコース（全六品） 先4000羊<br />\n又新鮮又好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAzHaWm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAzHaWm.png&h=558085cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P9xYtH2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP9xYtH2.png&h=f37154ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x857m23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx857m23.png&h=0e280376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JaaWfn4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJaaWfn4.png&h=c3650931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dACajPL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdACajPL.png&h=c14bda4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/37Ds6uM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F37Ds6uM.png&h=bc7a2d7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食飽飽就返去酒店 CHECK IN先 今次住呢間大江戶物語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r7tAvWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr7tAvWs.png&h=a61913ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身我自己去溫泉區都好少話會住呢D咁大型同埋連鎖式GE溫泉旅館<br />\n但因為城崎溫泉最主要都係去浸七個外湯 所以就試下 最主要唔貴<br />\n咁由於太早啦 我食完LUNCH都未夠三點 就係佢個LOBBY到坐陣先<br />\n咁佢有個位比人睇下漫畫咁 上下網咁 睇下電視 好快就夠三點啦<br />\n<br />\n住城崎溫泉旅館 佢都會比張PASS你 就係可以任去個七個外湯<br />\n<img src=\"https://stat.ameba.jp/user_images/20131217/23/616tomotomo/d2/59/j/o0480036012784035726.jpg?caw=800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstat.ameba.jp%2Fuser_images%2F20131217%2F23%2F616tomotomo%2Fd2%2F59%2Fj%2Fo0480036012784035726.jpg%3Fcaw%3D800&h=5b75fd80&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n無影到上網搵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2mN6uO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2mN6uO.png&h=d883bd78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後就出去浸溫泉<br />\n第一個就去左 駅舍溫泉さとの湯 <br />\n呢個係城崎溫泉站隔離 最大都係呢個外湯<br />\n入面乜鳩都有大浴場,露天風呂,仲有STEAM呀個D正到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.kinosaki-tajimaya.co.jp/tourism/1798957_475626975870244_2073288424_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kinosaki-tajimaya.co.jp%2Ftourism%2F1798957_475626975870244_2073288424_o.jpg&h=80c047e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://onsen.nifty.com/kk_image/view/onsen/onsen-detail/onsen003245/0000158149.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fonsen.nifty.com%2Fkk_image%2Fview%2Fonsen%2Fonsen-detail%2Fonsen003245%2F0000158149.jpg&h=a682e1b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後就返去食DINNER 自助餐都OK幾好食  D 蝦好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/haTQjQe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhaTQjQe.png&h=f96822c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完又出去浸過 <br />\n其他就有D比較大型 有D比較細 <br />\n最正都係駅舍溫泉さとの湯<br />\n最後我係全部七個浸哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c13gZQd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc13gZQd.png&h=8796a824&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrreMvg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrreMvg.png&h=170d8b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iJB6CUg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiJB6CUg.png&h=069b822a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/moJAweh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmoJAweh.png&h=f67a3465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cV8kHkY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcV8kHkY.png&h=09121fde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/48JAwef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F48JAwef.png&h=1e5423a3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n浸完就返去訓覺 聽日去天空之城<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一日完"},{"pid":"efe338eabb18967910fe773c8dea75d6e7242083","tid":949140,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:05:11.000Z","msg":"Good<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6238bf8afe88eace0c57edce98ebe5f0fe3b27","tid":949140,"uid":131280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:06:11.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e9e805ba259b9bd09422c095f1d86f31ff406ede","tid":949140,"uid":65130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:08:40.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"c243742a524b25ce54ca5ca23b1aded5d849fd8b","tid":949140,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:09:26.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"0fc5713237ab07ef03615e1025f2107d2a022de5","tid":949140,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:53:04.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"ef7f0f0d9c9bfbc68f54514c8f3950872c5df49e","tid":949140,"uid":149912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"90dd7e8d1151311224502b2082147de49e60e144","tid":949140,"uid":11254,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:02:54.000Z","msg":"DAY 1 <br />\n今次坐凌晨機  直接由關西機場去城崎溫泉<br />\n買個早餐先 最鐘意食個蛋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https:/