c=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r7tAvWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr7tAvWs.png&h=a61913ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身我自己去溫泉區都好少話會住呢D咁大型同埋連鎖式GE溫泉旅館<br />\n但因為城崎溫泉最主要都係去浸七個外湯 所以就試下 最主要唔貴<br />\n咁由於太早啦 我食完LUNCH都未夠三點 就係佢個LOBBY到坐陣先<br />\n咁佢有個位比人睇下漫畫咁 上下網咁 睇下電視 好快就夠三點啦<br />\n<br />\n住城崎溫泉旅館 佢都會比張PASS你 就係可以任去個七個外湯<br />\n<img src=\"https://stat.ameba.jp/user_images/20131217/23/616tomotomo/d2/59/j/o0480036012784035726.jpg?caw=800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstat.ameba.jp%2Fuser_images%2F20131217%2F23%2F616tomotomo%2Fd2%2F59%2Fj%2Fo0480036012784035726.jpg%3Fcaw%3D800&h=5b75fd80&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n無影到上網搵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2mN6uO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2mN6uO.png&h=d883bd78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後就出去浸溫泉<br />\n第一個就去左 駅舍溫泉さとの湯 <br />\n呢個係城崎溫泉站隔離 最大都係呢個外湯<br />\n入面乜鳩都有大浴場,露天風呂,仲有STEAM呀個D正到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.kinosaki-tajimaya.co.jp/tourism/1798957_475626975870244_2073288424_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kinosaki-tajimaya.co.jp%2Ftourism%2F1798957_475626975870244_2073288424_o.jpg&h=80c047e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://onsen.nifty.com/kk_image/view/onsen/onsen-detail/onsen003245/0000158149.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fonsen.nifty.com%2Fkk_image%2Fview%2Fonsen%2Fonsen-detail%2Fonsen003245%2F0000158149.jpg&h=a682e1b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後就返去食DINNER 自助餐都OK幾好食  D 蝦好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/haTQjQe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhaTQjQe.png&h=f96822c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完又出去浸過 <br />\n其他就有D比較大型 有D比較細 <br />\n最正都係駅舍溫泉さとの湯<br />\n最後我係全部七個浸哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c13gZQd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc13gZQd.png&h=8796a824&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrreMvg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrreMvg.png&h=170d8b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iJB6CUg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiJB6CUg.png&h=069b822a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/moJAweh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmoJAweh.png&h=f67a3465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cV8kHkY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcV8kHkY.png&h=09121fde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/48JAwef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F48JAwef.png&h=1e5423a3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n浸完就返去訓覺 聽日去天空之城<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一日完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T05:10:58.000Z","msg":"食蟹個間我前年食係&yen;3000六道菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b437803f463b1ad07a3b86faf8a0705d9d263874","tid":949140,"uid":182182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T15:58:37.000Z","msg":"留名待丁大不至"},{"pid":"60b75f63df1195a12f10a489f1992fb28f721f7a","tid":949140,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:28:16.000Z","msg":"DAY 2<br />\n<br />\n朝早起身就食個自助早餐先 之後就去浸溫泉<br />\n 雖然城崎溫泉出邊有得浸 但其實旅館個個都唔錯 <br />\n係細左小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  浸完食飽就再HEA陣<br />\n由於今日無咩行程  得一個 就係上竹田城 <br />\n所以差唔多成10點先CHECK OUT <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁間旅館同車站就有D距離 所以佢有接駁車去車站GE<br />\n咁由於仲未夠鐘搭車 就係附近行下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gWCmP6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgWCmP6c.jpg&h=aeb1866f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6HtAUs1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6HtAUs1.jpg&h=0eda6447&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買左呢個餅 好撚好食 好重牛味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆仲買左幾條蟹腳 話上車食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁差不多夠鐘就去搭車<br />\n<img src=\"https://d1itvcmfcfl6do.cloudfront.net/2015/08/Takeda_castle_07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd1itvcmfcfl6do.cloudfront.net%2F2015%2F08%2FTakeda_castle_07.jpg&h=4e5ef6da&s={SIZE}\" /> (網上圖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n要去睇雲海 姐係上邊呢個景 就要朝早5-6點上山GE<br />\n咁前一晚就要去最近立雲峽GE車站 分別有兩個 和田山同竹田站 <br />\n由於和田山附近多D旅館  所以就住係和田山<br />\n另外朝早上立雲峽係要BOOK 的士/自己揸車 咁我就訂左呢間叫有斐軒<br />\n因為網上睇話佢有得幫人BOOK 的士上山<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SVrF5EQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSVrF5EQ.jpg&h=d2648299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁佢入住時間係唔知二點定三點 我去到個陣先係一點左右 <br />\n本身諗住放低行李就走 點知個老闆娘勁好人 一早就比我CHECK IN  <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外老豆買左幾條蟹腳 佢仲幫我地雪住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後老闆娘就問 我地而加要去邊 去竹田城定立雲峽<br />\n我就話去竹田城 聽朝先去立雲峽 想麻煩佢幫手BOOK的士咁啦<br />\n點知 佢同我講話OK無問題 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bR5LxnK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbR5LxnK.jpg&h=04cbf6bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢老公聽日會車我地上山  而加車我地去竹田站 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解可以咁好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真係超級多謝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gwhh7Wf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgwhh7Wf.jpg&h=35f89aa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣去到竹田站呢 你想上竹田城有兩個選擇<br />\n一係行上去 二就係搭呢個天空巴士<br />\n<a href=\"http://wadayama.jp/takedajyoseki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwadayama.jp%2Ftakedajyoseki&d=fuxLroCnnWUwqjsasrgK4MVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=1a8aa065\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://wadayama.jp/takedajyoseki</a> <br />\n單程260 羊一日PASS 500 羊 無限上落<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SB3hov0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSB3hov0.jpg&h=7c3d5b28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上到山仲要行一陣先到個城<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/23/210819_be998eabe1b3f64968b3c74a26eed0b2.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F23%2F210819_be998eabe1b3f64968b3c74a26eed0b2.JPG&h=052b08bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kH5jBRD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkH5jBRD.jpg&h=2418bf08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n終於見到個城<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4m2Fmki.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4m2Fmki.jpg&h=5d7f9549&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上邊望落去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xiq0mkE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXiq0mkE.jpg&h=c45d6b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oBa7LNC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoBa7LNC.jpg&h=d5442faa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tMLoi75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtMLoi75.jpg&h=00163e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影返個城<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TUcVafd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTUcVafd.jpg&h=f586e482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RvXeqOX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRvXeqOX.jpg&h=0c5dc43a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f1bKN3u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff1bKN3u.jpg&h=b9317c21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hb3hoBS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhb3hoBS.jpg&h=06145902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影到咁上下 就搭車返去食晚餐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YBmVUJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYBmVUJY.jpg&h=792cf21c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老闆娘已經準備好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲幫我地今日買個D蟹腳分好哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcok5Q1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxcok5Q1.jpg&h=b4160294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HSipN4o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHSipN4o.jpg&h=22a21610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ADpsLQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FADpsLQ4.jpg&h=579e03f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食飽飽 休息一陣就訓覺 聽日好早起身上山<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDAY 2 完"},{"pid":"edd187fe6ab78cc90d2ecdd8adf171a8fc3b0552","tid":949140,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:29:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食蟹個間我前年食係&yen;3000六道菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我4000都覺得抵 <br />\n3000<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e436a5d3cef3115ebec54b0530850223530f2f18","tid":949140,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0371b22ef29b9bb067ff33693c07036ce4914d","tid":949140,"uid":40771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:49:19.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c60fea4c2a9d971de12f69439f30090b822e4a","tid":949140,"uid":44318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:14:50.000Z","msg":"孝子文識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4723ce4a2447cdad942c191341ef4990e54550f5","tid":949140,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98c60fea4c2a9d971de12f69439f30090b822e4a","tid":949140,"uid":44318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:14:50.000Z","msg":"孝子文識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:16:51.000Z","msg":"咪推啦CHING"},{"pid":"e100737e00f8276fb2cfa2623bd17aaa5ed5a14e","tid":949140,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ccfb0f214c0d7a6329c39780d8f19beb128408","tid":949140,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:27:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老味牙去2日？"},{"pid":"dedb09dbfe3f932915b45009ad965db0e7b41dcf","tid":949140,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23ccfb0f214c0d7a6329c39780d8f19beb128408","tid":949140,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:27:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老味牙去2日？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:32:28.000Z","msg":"關唔關你事呀利狗"},{"pid":"61814bbe6f8b397c061bed520c8627abb8ecd0ee","tid":949140,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T13:26:40.000Z","msg":"Day 3 <br />\n<br />\n由於要上山睇雲海 所以一早就要搭車 <br />\n本身如果係我book 的士會book 5點左右<br />\n但由於係民宿免費車我地上山 就唔麻煩人地了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過上到山已經見到好多日本人係山上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sqt33yL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsqt33yL.png&h=ee7d83d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開始見到個城仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n理想：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6LizqPD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6LizqPD.png&h=3378a4bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LLprgWj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLLprgWj.png&h=827f1749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現實：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjGQJz3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjGQJz3.png&h=901d4007&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cmOoi8p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcmOoi8p.png&h=04d03a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRyfUGL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRyfUGL.png&h=af94e91d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFESctr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFESctr.png&h=96b31f58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知係咪太遲上山 雲海就睇唔到 不過都算好天 睇到下個城 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就返落山食早餐 <br />\n由於只係有車去程  無回程 所以我地係要行返落山搭JR先返到去間旅館 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C7jScvx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC7jScvx.png&h=8a1435de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vcEVUJT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvcEVUJT.png&h=74911c8b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nB9F5Qz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnB9F5Qz.png&h=d3aa0ca7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tmFYSvB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtmFYSvB.png&h=f4b0898d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pAmQhh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pAmQhh.png&h=88bdcfa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沿路都幾靚 d樹好撚高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oe5VahP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOe5VahP.png&h=bceb7fcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行完山好攰返到去有早餐食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完就同民宿主人講拜拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢仲車我地出和田山站 超好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後下午就去國寶姬路城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2521f60098a948befb4b26322ec3efd995fc3868","tid":949140,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T13:33:23.000Z","msg":"十卜"},{"pid":"3ebe27a7d328101c49b8f28898daf4fcca4dc9de","tid":949140,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"返到去姬路就check in放底行李<br />\n今次住一間叫蒙特利酒店 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NjpScE8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNjpScE8.png&h=ab4629ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢係日本有好多分店 呢間姬路城店係新開 又平又靚 仲有大浴場 係姬路城隔離幾分鐘就到 超方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n放底完d行李 之後就行去姬路城<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Pyccyi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Pyccyi.png&h=ab1cbe84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行到去門口有好多銀杏樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gtYC76E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgtYC76E.png&h=e37f7cde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qn3ojdk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQn3ojdk.png&h=8c623e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFNTGrG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFNTGrG.png&h=50291580&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uQFueMH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuQFueMH.png&h=20b39187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姬路城真係好撚尾機 外面睇已經咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就入城上天守閣 之前都去過咩大阪城 松江城個d 但都無上過去 今次特登上去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入去要除鞋 之後就行d木梯上最頂 <br />\n唔知其他城係咪咁 但姬路城天守閣入面好有feel <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有d文物 忍者房個d睇下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q5SPZeR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq5SPZeR.png&h=d98fc3c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sRH8vmx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsRH8vmx.png&h=5af3da3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上到最高望返落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z8XHzOd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ8XHzOd.png&h=6278301c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wfFNLUV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwfFNLUV.png&h=7dfd996f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FN4VUOg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFN4VUOg.png&h=d52faffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後落返去再影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白鷺城真係好撚靚 去完之後我諗其他城都未必會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 差太遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ZSkmwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ZSkmwW.png&h=86662f0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsGtvqh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgsGtvqh.png&h=d38c6f2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個燒蠔係姬路城出邊 幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QDKKObY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQDKKObY.png&h=0cc6fda7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n返去姬路站 返去大浴場浸下 就完第三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2baaa1732630a33129961323b44be4be30478e","tid":949140,"uid":44318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T13:57:48.000Z","msg":"留名自己去"},{"pid":"83bcc6a37dd0c3d628439137d0595e272a806541","tid":949140,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:30:27.000Z","msg":"推到day4"},{"pid":"5a91832e8ebfeabc8d45d27bee4d94fa2eb4b1b6","tid":949140,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83bcc6a37dd0c3d628439137d0595e272a806541","tid":949140,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:30:27.000Z","msg":"推到day4"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:32:31.000Z","msg":"收嗲"},{"pid":"e8b71223fb47ec63ae3d1c03acf5d07a11dcf9c9","tid":949140,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e2baaa1732630a33129961323b44be4be30478e","tid":949140,"uid":44318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T13:57:48.000Z","msg":"留名自己去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:1